item.title: SoftLayer_Network_Tunnel_Module_Context
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_Tunnel_Module_Context Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_Tunnel_Module_Context data type contains general information relating to a single SoftLayer network tunnel. The SoftLayer_Network_Tunnel_Module_Context is useful to gather information such as related customer subnets (remote) and internal subnets (local) associated with the network tunnel as well as other information needed to manage the network tunnel. Account and billing information related to the network tunnel can also be retrieved. Local accountId A network tunnel's account identifier.
